data.name: angLightDirection.ToolTip
data.value: This controls the light direction, specified as an Azimuth angle, where north is 0 and the angle increases clockwise.

data.name: dbxElevationFactor.ToolTip
data.value: This factor defaults to a value that converts feet into degrees of latitude and longitude. If your elevation and projection are the same unit, this should be 1. If your elevation is in feet but your projection is meters, this should be about .3048

data.name: btnQuick.ToolTip
data.value: Choose from some predefined raster symbologies.

data.name: btnRamp.ToolTip
data.value: Builds a sequential ramp of colors instead of random colors

data.name: cmdRefresh.ToolTip
data.value: Regenerates all the colors randomly, using the same original categories.
